front.title: •3B3-1204
front.gametext: While with two other battle droids, may use 1 Force to target an opponent's Jedi present. Target's immunity to attrition is canceled for remainder of turn.
front.lore: Infantry battle droid programmed with anti-Jedi combat tactics by the blockade flagship. Was to begin uploading his program to the rest of the unit when the Jedi escaped.

cancels: Immunity to attrition of a Jedi
